2017 WW15 Bakerville/SKX-D BKC Release Announcement (BKC #14)

\n \n \n

DEG Platform Integration Team

\n \n
\n

The DEG platform Integration team announces the release of 2017 WW15 Bakerville/SKX-D BKC release package for Intel internal use. The release is based on OS of\n \n ESXi6.5/\n \n RHEL7.3/\n \n WS2016\n server. The auto-installer packages are available in the Artifactory server (both SH site and OR site). Any questions please contact Bei, Ling.

Test Result:

l  Finish BKC test execution on RHEL7.3-BU2 , Windows2016 and VMware ESXi6.5. Please visit HPQC for test details. Refer to the installation\nguide for the BKC package installation

l  Bakerville(RP Board: Yuba\nCity RP fab3)

o   Total test cases: 95; Passed test\ncases is 87 and pass rate is 91.58%.

    SKX-D ES2 SoC(QMXT, QMXS): Run P1 and P2 test cases, power cycling and Power & Performance test.

         SKX-D ES2 SoC(QN5Z): run boot up test.
